Burn-Murdoch</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> Murdoch has many other pieces of data to back up the conclusion, and Silver has some poll aggregates that confirm the story.</p><p> Nor is this a case of Hispanic and Black leftists being angry at Biden over Israel. The nonwhite voters shifting toward the GOP almost all self-identify as conservatives: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97950d22-5a1f-463a-b4ed-6dfee815a3cf_1280x846.jpeg" width="706" height="466.621875" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/pub